reviewText: Hello mob fan's This is a nice movie about the extreme action's one of power takes once robbed .Typically if you steal from the mob your done for,the case is no different here but the characters envolved ,especially the poor struggling family bring you into thier painful sometimes dysfunctional lives ,like many mob movies the end is operatic , not since The Funeral have I seen so tragic an ending,it certianly does surprise you.
